WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.066 --> 00:00:02.950
Symbolic forms and inscriptions.

00:00:02.950 --> 00:00:05.800
These are my life's work.

00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:08.350
As my knowledge grew,

00:00:08.350 --> 00:00:11.350
I also began to see similar shapes among the stars.

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:15.350
In that instant, I made up my mind to become

00:00:15.916 --> 00:00:17.233
a Rune Seeker.

00:00:18.550 --> 00:00:23.150
As Farrow just explained, runes are a very powerful ancient inscription that

00:00:23.150 --> 00:00:26.350
can be inlaid into your items to give them greater power.

00:00:26.900 --> 00:00:30.300
During the Alliance period, engraving shapes on relics will allow you to choose from

00:00:30.300 --> 00:00:33.983
several different crafting runes, enabling you to enhance your items.

00:00:34.633 --> 00:00:38.183
When you encounter a relic, it will have two to seven

00:00:38.733 --> 00:00:39.866
slots. The

00:00:39.866 --> 00:00:42.783
more slots you have, the more difficult the relics will be,

00:00:42.783 --> 00:00:45.450
but you will also have more options.

00:00:45.450 --> 00:00:47.333
At the start of the game, you may

00:00:47.333 --> 00:00:49.400
craft some simple damage or resistance runes,

00:00:49.750 --> 00:00:51.116
which you can acquire at a lower level than you would normally obtain them

00:00:51.116 --> 00:00:52.616
,

00:00:52.700 --> 00:00:54.433
giving you a considerable power boost.

00:00:54.650 --> 00:00:56.516
But things will soon get interesting. There are

00:00:57.250 --> 00:01:00.233
a total of 22 new runes that affect rune protection, and

00:01:00.483 --> 00:01:02.450
a brand new resource that will prevent you from dying.

00:01:03.033 --> 00:01:06.900
Using these runes will give you additional defensive capabilities, or you can

00:01:06.900 --> 00:01:10.150
convert your runic protection into offensive weapons through the Kargo rune ability.

00:01:13.183 --> 00:01:16.600
Additionally, there are 13 runes that enhance specific weapon types,

00:01:16.800 --> 00:01:19.833
such as this rune that gives grenades a chance to explode a second time.

00:01:21.283 --> 00:01:24.566
Or this one, which will grant you a

00:01:24.616 --> 00:01:26.200
new buff called "Druidic Blessing" when you severely stun your enemies.

00:01:28.950 --> 00:01:29.850
Above that,

00:01:29.850 --> 00:01:32.850
there are 22 runes designed to give you power at lower levels,

00:01:32.850 --> 00:01:35.850
such as this one, which will give you a lot of elemental resistance, or

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:38.683
this one, which will give you a lot of spirit.

00:01:38.683 --> 00:01:42.300
These runes are intentionally designed to be quite powerful, but they will gradually weaken as you level up.

00:01:42.300 --> 00:01:45.300
These will be excellent tools for you when you're rebuilding in the league.

00:01:45.733 --> 00:01:47.933
We also have 6 runes that can be used to expand the potential affix pool when crafting high-tier items

00:01:47.933 --> 00:01:51.016
.

00:01:51.600 --> 00:01:55.133
For example, you can socket "Kathra's Sorrow" onto some gloves,

00:01:55.133 --> 00:01:58.516
which can then be used to create a whole new set of vanishing-related affixes for

00:01:58.600 --> 00:02:00.650
damage over time builds.

00:02:01.216 --> 00:02:03.316
After socketing a rune of this type,

00:02:03.316 --> 00:02:06.416
you can use ordinary Exalted or Chaos Stones to create new affixes.

00:02:08.666 --> 00:02:10.583
Some runes also provide a powerful effect to items,

00:02:10.583 --> 00:02:13.900
but they are permanently locked in the slot.

00:02:14.066 --> 00:02:17.183
For example, this one provides an additional suffix to any item.

00:02:21.200 --> 00:02:23.516
Or this one, which allows you to create a jewelry slot.

00:02:29.166 --> 00:02:30.400
Or perhaps this rune series

00:02:30.400 --> 00:02:33.566
can transfer any element affix from one element to another.

00:02:34.933 --> 00:02:37.700
There is even a rune that can upgrade other runes,

00:02:37.700 --> 00:02:39.750
allowing you to upgrade them to levels that are normally unattainable.

00:02:42.133 --> 00:02:45.133
In closing, I would like to present "Adel's Legacy" to you all.

00:02:45.433 --> 00:02:50.266
It is a special rune that can be socketed into any Kal'god or Ezma legendary item to destroy that item

00:02:50.266 --> 00:02:53.233
and create a new rune that draws some of the legendary item's power.

00:02:53.816 --> 00:02:54.983
For example,

00:02:54.983 --> 00:02:58.350
use this rune on "Shoes of Trampling" to create a "Legacy Shoes of Trampling" rune.

00:02:58.500 --> 00:02:59.950
When it is socketed into any shoe,

00:02:59.950 --> 00:03:01.683
just like the legendary item from which it originates,

00:03:01.683 --> 00:03:05.233
you will deal damage equal to 10% of the overflow damage to enemies within 2 meters of the killed enemy.

00:03:05.983 --> 00:03:08.700
Or perhaps "Legacy: Aberrant Dome"?

00:03:08.700 --> 00:03:10.466
Destroying an "Aberrant Dome"

00:03:10.466 --> 00:03:13.666
will add cold damage based on maximum mana to any weapon.

00:03:14.783 --> 00:03:17.900
Through "Adel's Legacy," you can create hundreds more runes,

00:03:17.900 --> 00:03:19.950
covering the effects of various legendary items. At

00:03:22.516 --> 00:03:25.116
this point, you might be thinking, "Wow, there are really a lot of new runes!"

00:03:25.116 --> 00:03:26.350
And you're right.

00:03:26.350 --> 00:03:28.350
After all, this is "Adel's Rune".

00:03:28.350 --> 00:03:31.000
But we don't want the old runes to fall behind. A

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:32.700
considerable number of old runes that were not used much

00:03:32.700 --> 00:03:34.800
were also enhanced,

00:03:34.800 --> 00:03:37.233
significantly optimizing the crafting system. Explore all the possibilities that runes bring

00:03:37.566 --> 00:03:39.183
in the "Ancient Return" update released on May 30th (Taiwan time).

00:03:39.183 --> 00:03:42.883
See you then!

